 the additional just makes it breakeven on the TCE over a longer period of time hurting the PnL as well."},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-11T21:55:12.39","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"demurrage updated and interim port deviation ended up higher than expected"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-03-01T21:32:43.41","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"updated port cost bahamas...now on our account due change in rotation est at $74k"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-02-24T21:44:39.37","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"change in orders again -- kingston fb nassau"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-02-23T19:05:13.327","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Discharge orders changed Interim port now for Curacao/Bahamas"}],"offhireList":[{"id":190667,"dateStartUtc":null,"dateEndUtc":null,"days":null,"displayOrder":0,"offhireReason":null,"remark":null,"offhireBunkerList":[{"id":55812,"gradeName":"LSBF","quantity":null,"price":null,"displayOrder":0}]}],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}